xplicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Amir\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7678:\"<p><strong>WPML&#8217;s <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/translating-your-contents/using-the-translation-editor/\">Translation Management</a> lets you control who translates each piece of content, to what languages. But sometimes, you need to set up something simpler, like allowing a certain user to edit all content in a specific language. Today, we explain how to do this using <a href=\"https://wp-types.com/home/types-access/\">Access</a> plugin, which you get for free with your WPML account</strong>.</p>\n<h2>1. Sign-up for a complementary Types+Access account</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://wp-types.com/home/types-access/\">Access</a> plugin is part of the <a href=\"https://wp-types.com\">Toolset</a> package. We offer Access for free, to all WPML clients, so that you can control access to specific languages in multilingual sites.</p>\n<p>Log in to your <a href=\"https://wpml.org/account/\">WPML.org account</a>. You will see a &#8216;Toolset&#8217; section. If it&#8217;s collapsed, expand it and click to &#8216;get Access&#8217; for free.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_784401\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/get-access-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"Get Access\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-784401\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/get-access-300x169.jpg 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/get-access-768x433.jpg 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/get-access.jpg 970w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Get Access</p></div>\n<h2>2. Download and install Access</h2>\n<p>If you already have a Toolset account, you don&#8217;t need this. Go to your account and download Access.</p>\n<p>Log in to your <a href=\"https://wp-types.com/account/\">Toolset account</a>, click on Downloads and download Access. It&#8217;s a plugin, so you need to upload Access to your &#8216;plugins&#8217; folder and activate it.</p>\n<h2>3. Use Access plugin to grant permissions for users in languages</h2>\n<p>Go to the Access menu, in the WordPress admin and select &#8216;manage by Access&#8217; next to the content types that you want.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_745997\" style=\"width: 563px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/04.books-cpt-managed-by-access.png\" alt=\"Allow Access to manage the content type\" width=\"553\" height=\"192\" class=\"size-full wp-image-745997\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/04.books-cpt-managed-by-access-150x52.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/04.books-cpt-managed-by-access-300x104.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/04.books-cpt-managed-by-access.png 553w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 553px) 100vw, 553px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Allow Access to manage the content type</p></div>\n<p>Next, click on the button:<br />\n<strong>Add permission for languages</strong> at the bottom of the access admin screen, just before the <strong>Custom Roles</strong> section.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_784410\" style=\"width: 496px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/enable-permissions-for-languages.jpg\" alt=\"Enable permissions for languages\" width=\"486\" height=\"212\" class=\"size-full wp-image-784410\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/enable-permissions-for-languages-300x131.jpg 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/enable-permissions-for-languages.jpg 486w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 486px) 100vw, 486px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Enable permissions for languages</p></div>\n<p>Now, you will see a list of languages to enable. Select the language, to which you want to give privileges.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_745998\" style=\"width: 521px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/05.books-cpt-create-language-group.png\" alt=\"Creating a new group of permissions\" width=\"511\" height=\"314\" class=\"size-full wp-image-745998\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/05.books-cpt-create-language-group-150x92.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/05.books-cpt-create-language-group-300x184.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/05.books-cpt-create-language-group.png 511w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 511px) 100vw, 511px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Creating a new group of permissions</p></div>\n<p>This will display a complete set of permissions matrix for the post type, in the selected languages. Access plugin gives you fine-grained controls over user permissions. Don&#8217;t worry about the number of options. Access will also help you make sure that all required permissions are enabled, to achieve what you need.</p>\n<p>Finally, select the permissions that you&#8217;d like to add.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_745999\" style=\"width: 955px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/06.books-cpt-set-permissions-for-german-language.png\" alt=\"Giving permissions to language editor\" width=\"945\" height=\"624\" class=\"size-full wp-image-745999\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/06.books-cpt-set-permissions-for-german-language-150x99.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/06.books-cpt-set-permissions-for-german-language-300x198.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/06.books-cpt-set-permissions-for-german-language.png 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 945px) 100vw, 945px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Giving permissions to language editor</p></div>\n<p>You can add the permissions to an entire role (which you can create in Access), or to specific users. To grant the permissions to a specific user, enter the username in the last column of the permission you want to grant.</p>\n<p>Remember to save.</p>\n<p>And, you&#8217;re done. The users to whom you granted permissions can now do everything in that language. This way, you can create users who can edit and publish content in specific languages.</p>\n<h2>Works with and without Translation Management</h2>\n<p>You can use Access plugin in any site running WPML, with or without Translation Management. If you are using Translation Management, you will be able to send content to translation and set-up a user who will work as &#8216;editor/proofreader&#8217;. If you don&#8217;t use Translation Management, you will be able to allow certain users to translate content to different languages.</p>\n<h2>Feedback?</h2>\n<p>Both <a href=\"/\">WPML</a> and <a href=\"https://wp-types.com\">Toolset</a> teams have worked hard to make this feature complete and easy to use. We&#8217;d love to hear your feedback.</p>\n<p><strong>If you have comments, suggestions or questions, leave your questions and we&#8217;ll get back to you.</strong></p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=qYjmAihw1lo:ehlXuTkjV8I:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=qYjmAihw1lo:ehlXuTkjV8I:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=qYjmAihw1lo:ehlXuTkjV8I:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=qYjmAihw1lo:ehlXuTkjV8I:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=qYjmAihw1lo:ehlXuTkjV8I:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=qYjmAihw1lo:ehlXuTkjV8I:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/qYjmAihw1lo\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://wpml.org/2016/01/allow-certain-users-edit-specific-languages/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"16\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://wpml.org/2016/01/allow-certain-users-edit-specific-languages/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:114:\"This week Compatible – Rubbez, Magnium, JobMonster, PE Cooking Blog, Display Posts Shortcode, Magic Post Listing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/5i451f1uZcI/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:139:\"https://wpml.org/2016/01/this-week-compatible-rubbez-magnium-jobmonster-pe-cooking-blog-display-posts-shortcode-magic-post-listing/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 07 Jan 2016 19:41:19 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"Compatibility Bulletin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"https://wpml.org/?p=782938\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:330:\"So we are all back from our winter holidays, ready to announce some great themes and plugins that were tested and found compatible with WPML: Today we are happy to announce that we have 4 themes and 2 plugins to add to our compatibility list. The themes are Rubbez, Magnium, JobMonster, PE Cooking Blog and the plugins [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Amit\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6777:\"<p>So we are all back from our winter holidays, ready to announce some great themes and plugins that were tested and found compatible with WPML:</p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce that we have 4 themes and 2 plugins to add to our compatibility list. The themes are <a title=\"Rubbez\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/rubbez-woocommerce-corporate-responsive-theme/9537633\">Rubbez</a>, <a title=\"Magnium\" href=\"http://magniumthemes.com/themes/magnium/\">Magnium</a>, <a title=\"JobMonster\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/jobmonster-job-board-wordpress-theme/10965446\">JobMonster</a>, <a title=\"PE Cooking Blog\" href=\"https://www.pixelemu.com/themes/i/8-food-a-drink/1-pe-cooking-blog\">PE Cooking Blog</a> and the plugins are <a title=\"Display Posts Shortcode\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/display-posts-shortcode\">Display Posts Shortcode</a>, <a title=\"Magic Post Listing\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/magic-post-listing/\">Magic Post Listing</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Themes \" href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Plugins \" href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title=\"Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins\" href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Rubbez theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/rubbez-woocommerce-corporate-responsive-theme/9537633\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/rubbez.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Rubbez is a new WordPress theme for Online Shopping, Corporate and Travel website.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/rubbez-woocommerce-corporate-responsive-theme/9537633\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Rubbez theme</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Magnium theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://magniumthemes.com/themes/magnium/\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/magnium.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Magnium theme is a multipurpose WordPress themes on Themeforest. This theme can be used for any personal or business needs to easy create and launch your WordPress based website in several minutes</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://magniumthemes.com/themes/magnium/\">Purchase Magnium theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">JobMonster theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/jobmonster-job-board-wordpress-theme/10965446\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/jobmonster.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Jobmonster is the functional Job Board WordPress Theme with gorgeous layout and exclusive job board system to connect candidates and employers fluidly.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/jobmonster-job-board-wordpress-theme/10965446\">Purchase JobMonster theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">PE Cooking Blog theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.pixelemu.com/themes/i/8-food-a-drink/1-pe-cooking-blog\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/pe.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>The theme is addressed for everybody looking for excellent wordpress cooking theme for posting your own food recipes as well as for the site of many recipes submitters.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.pixelemu.com/themes/i/8-food-a-drink/1-pe-cooking-blog\">Purchase PE Cooking Blog theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Display Posts Shortcode plugin</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/display-posts-shortcode/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/dps.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Display a listing of posts using the [display-posts] shortcode\n</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/display-posts-shortcode/\">Download Display Posts Shortcode plugin</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Magic Post Listing plugin</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/magic-post-listing/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/mpl.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>A plugin for creating content sliders and image sliders\n</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/magic-post-listing/\">Download Magic Post Listing plugin</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=5i451f1uZcI:jzhD_fKhRVQ:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~